The evidence with the title 'EPA's wood-burning stove ban has chilling consequences for ... ' says Jan 29, 2014  ... The EPA has recently banned the production and sale of 80 percent of America 's current wood - burning stoves , the oldest heating method known tomankind ... Governments in some states have gone even further than EPA , not only banning the sale of noncompliant stoves , but even their use as fireplaces . 
